# Workspace Plan Location

When creating or updating plan files for this repository:

- Always create plan files under `.cursor/plans` inside the workspace root.
- Do not store project plans only in global locations (for example under `~/.cursor/plans`) without also copying them into the workspace.
- Prefer stable, descriptive plan filenames so they are easy to find in the repository.
- After a plan is fully executed, ask the user whether the plan should be moved to `.cursor/plans/done`.
